No.

18
00:02:40,139 --> 00:02:42,141
It's not a date.

19
00:02:43,044 --> 00:02:45,544
No way. Miwako, even you don't know

20
00:02:45,544 --> 00:02:47,144
where Officer Takagi is going?

21
